description:
Add string constants for the workflow enum values in internal/tick/tick.go

Create constants for type safety and consistency:

// Requires values
const (
    RequiresApproval = "approval"
    RequiresReview   = "review"
    RequiresContent  = "content"
)

// Awaiting values
const (
    AwaitingWork       = "work"
    AwaitingApproval   = "approval"
    AwaitingInput      = "input"
    AwaitingReview     = "review"
    AwaitingContent    = "content"
    AwaitingEscalation = "escalation"
    AwaitingCheckpoint = "checkpoint"
)

// Verdict values
const (
    VerdictApproved = "approved"
    VerdictRejected = "rejected"
)

Also add helper slices for validation:
- ValidRequiresValues []string
- ValidAwaitingValues []string
- ValidVerdictValues []string
